it when something happens.

00:37:07.990 --> 00:37:10.680
And that's why we're also
more sort of open source.

00:37:10.680 --> 00:37:13.190
So this is something that if
you want to run your own Crisis

00:37:13.190 --> 00:37:14.770
Map, you can run
your own Crisis Map.

00:37:14.770 --> 00:37:17.450
If you want to run your
own Person Finder, you can.

00:37:17.450 --> 00:37:20.910
